<concept id="dg-uppercase-function">
  <title>The <codeph>oxy_uppercase()</codeph> Function</title>
  <conbody>
    <p>The <codeph>oxy_uppercase()</codeph> function transforms to upper case the text received as
      argument.</p>
    <syntaxdiagram>
      <groupseq>
        <kwd>oxy_uppercase</kwd>
        <sep>(</sep>
        <kwd> text </kwd>
        <sep>)</sep>
      </groupseq>
    </syntaxdiagram>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>text</dt>
        <dd>The text to be capitalized.</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
    <example>
      <p>To insert as static text content before each element its upper-cased qualified name, use
        this CSS
        selector:<codeblock outputclass="language-css">*:before{
  content: oxy_uppercase(oxy_name()) ": ";
}</codeblock></p>
    </example>
  </conbody>
</concept>